---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import LegacyHeader from '../components/LegacyHeader.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import ContactSection from '../components/ContactSection.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import ButtonPrimary from '../components/ButtonPrimary.astro';
import ButtonSecondary from '../components/ButtonSecondary.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Expert Gaming SEO Services | Bright Forge SEO" description="Gaming SEO services that level up your online presence and drive more players to your games. Bright Forge SEO specializes in gaming industry strategies.">
  <LegacyHeader slot="header" />

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <Hero
    badgeIcon="fas fa-gamepad"
    badgeText="Gaming SEO Specialists"
    title="Gaming SEO Services That Level Up Your Online Presence"
    breadcrumbCurrent="Gaming SEO Services"
  >
    <Fragment slot="story">
      <p>Ready to dominate the gaming industry's search rankings? At Bright Forge <a href="/">SEO Agency</a>, we understand the unique challenges of marketing gaming businesses. From indie game developers to major gaming studios, we craft specialized SEO strategies that drive more players, increase downloads, and boost your gaming brand's visibility in this competitive digital landscape.</p>
    </Fragment>

    <Fragment slot="actions">
      <ButtonPrimary href="/contact/" text="Start Your Gaming SEO Quest" />
      <ButtonSecondary href="#services" text="Explore Our Services" />
    </Fragment>

    <Fragment slot="visual">
      <div class="hero-image-container">
        <div class="gaming-icon-grid">
          <div class="gaming-icon"><i class="fas fa-gamepad"></i></div>
          <div class="gaming-icon"><i class="fas fa-trophy"></i></div>
          <div class="gaming-icon"><i class="fas fa-rocket"></i></div>
          <div class="gaming-icon"><i class="fas fa-users"></i></div>
          <div class="gaming-icon"><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i></div>
          <div class="gaming-icon"><i class="fas fa-star"></i></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Fragment>
  </Hero>

  <!-- Why Gaming SEO Section -->
  <section class="why-gaming-section">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Why Gaming Businesses Need <span>Specialized SEO</span></h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="gaming-explanation">
        <div class="gaming-card">
          <div class="gaming-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="gaming-text">
            <p>The gaming industry is incredibly competitive, with millions of games, apps, and gaming-related content fighting for attention. Generic SEO strategies simply don't cut it in this space. You need specialized knowledge of gaming keywords, player behavior, gaming platforms, and the unique search patterns of gamers.</p>
            
            <p>Our gaming SEO expertise helps you connect with your target audience—whether they're casual mobile gamers, hardcore PC enthusiasts, console players, or esports fans. We understand the gaming ecosystem and craft strategies that speak directly to your players' search habits.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Key Features Section -->
  <section class="features-section">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>What Makes Our Gaming <span>SEO Services</span> Legendary</h2>
        <p>We combine deep gaming industry knowledge with proven SEO strategies to deliver results that matter</p>
      </div>

      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-gamepad"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Gaming Industry Expertise</h3>
          <p>We live and breathe gaming culture. Our team understands gaming terminology, trends, platforms, and player psychology. This insider knowledge translates into SEO strategies that resonate with your gaming audience.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-search"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Platform-Specific Optimization</h3>
          <p>From Steam and Epic Games Store to mobile app stores and gaming websites, we optimize for the platforms where your audience discovers games. Each platform has unique ranking factors we leverage for maximum visibility.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Data-Driven Results</h3>
          <p>We track metrics that matter to gaming businesses: download rates, user acquisition costs, player engagement, and lifetime value. Our SEO strategies are designed to improve these key performance indicators.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Community-Focused Approach</h3>
          <p>Gaming is all about community. We help you build and engage with your player base through content marketing, social SEO, and community-driven link building strategies that gaming audiences love.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Multi-Platform Strategy</h3>
          <p>Whether you're targeting mobile gamers, PC enthusiasts, or console players, we create comprehensive SEO strategies that work across all gaming platforms and devices.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Services for Gaming Teams -->
  <section id="services" class="services-offerings-section">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Services Built For <span>Gaming Teams</span></h2>
        <p>From solo indies to established studios and publishers, we tailor our SEO to how players actually search and discover games.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="offerings-grid">
        <div class="offering-card">
          <div class="offering-icon"><i class="fas fa-store"></i></div>
          <h3>Store Listing Optimization (ASO + SEO)</h3>
          <p>Optimize your Steam, App Store, and Google Play pages for search and conversion. We refine titles, short/long descriptions, tags, screenshots, and trailers to earn more wishlists and installs.</p>
          <a class="learn-more-link" href="/keyword-research-services/">Keyword Research</a>
        </div>

        <div class="offering-card">
          <div class="offering-icon"><i class="fas fa-cogs"></i></div>
          <h3>Technical SEO for Gaming Sites</h3>
          <p>Faster loads, cleaner architecture, and structured markup across landing pages, wikis, and patch hubs. We improve Core Web Vitals and crawling so players land where they should.</p>
          <a class="learn-more-link" href="/seo-audit-services/">SEO Audits</a>
        </div>

        <div class="offering-card">
          <div class="offering-icon"><i class="fas fa-scroll"></i></div>
          <h3>Content That Gamers Search For</h3>
          <p>Guides, build write‑ups, boss strategies, progression tips, patch notes, and FAQs — written for humans first, structured for search engines second.</p>
          <a class="learn-more-link" href="/content-seo-services-philippines/">Content SEO</a>
        </div>

        <div class="offering-card">
          <div class="offering-icon"><i class="fas fa-users"></i></div>
          <h3>Community & UGC SEO</h3>
          <p>Reddit, Discord, YouTube, and wiki ecosystems already talk about your game. We help you earn links naturally, index the right threads, and turn UGC into a discoverability engine.</p>
          <a class="learn-more-link" href="/backlink-seo-services-philippines/">Link Earning</a>
        </div>

        <div class="offering-card">
          <div class="offering-icon"><i class="fab fa-youtube"></i></div>
          <h3>YouTube & Creator SEO</h3>
          <p>From official trailers to how‑to videos and devlogs, we optimize titles, thumbnails, descriptions, and chaptering so players actually find and watch your content.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="offering-card">
          <div class="offering-icon"><i class="fas fa-globe"></i></div>
          <h3>International & Localization</h3>
          <p>Multi‑language store pages and websites with proper hreflang, translated metadata, and cultural keyword research to meet players where they are.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="offering-card">
          <div class="offering-icon"><i class="fas fa-code"></i></div>
          <h3>Schema & Rich Results</h3>
          <p>Game, VideoObject, HowTo, Product, and SoftwareApplication schema to power rich results, knowledge panels, and better SERP real estate for your brand.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="offering-card">
          <div class="offering-icon"><i class="fas fa-chart-pie"></i></div>
          <h3>Analytics & Measurement</h3>
          <p>We connect the dots between organic discovery and in‑game outcomes — wishlist to purchase, demo to install, and the content that actually moves players.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How We Work -->
  <section class="approach-section gaming-approach">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>How We <span>Work</span> With Gaming Teams</h2>
        <p>Simple process. Clear deliverables. Built for the realities of game development.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="steps-grid">
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-number">1</div>
          <h3>Discovery & Alignment</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Understand your game, audience, platform, and milestones</li>
            <li>Audit site/store presence and competitors</li>
            <li>Create goals for wishlist, install, and community growth</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-number">2</div>
          <h3>Technical & Platform Optimization</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Fix crawl, indexation, and Web Vitals issues</li>
            <li>Optimize Steam/App Store/Google Play assets</li>
            <li>Implement schema and internal linking</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-number">3</div>
          <h3>Content & Community</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Editorial calendar for guides, updates, and devlogs</li>
            <li>YouTube SEO and creator collaboration guidelines</li>
            <li>Earn links via news beats, assets, and helpful resources</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-number">4</div>
          <h3>Measure & Iterate</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Dashboards tying discovery to installs and revenue</li>
            <li>Quarterly roadmaps with prioritized improvements</li>
            <li>Continuous testing across titles and regions</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Launch Timeline -->
  <section class="launch-timeline-section">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>SEO For <span>Pre‑Launch → Live Ops</span></h2>
        <p>We plug into your roadmap. The work shifts as you move from announcement to launch to ongoing updates.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-grid">
        <div class="timeline-card">
          <div class="timeline-badge">Pre‑Launch</div>
          <h3>Build Discoverability Early</h3>
          <p>Secure brand terms, create a fast landing page, and seed guide topics so your future players can find you. Optimize your store coming soon page for wishlists.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-card">
          <div class="timeline-badge">Beta</div>
          <h3>Feedback → Content</h3>
          <p>Turn feedback into searchable FAQs, patch notes, and video explainers. Surface bug fix updates and new features clearly in search.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-card">
          <div class="timeline-badge">Launch</div>
          <h3>Own The SERP</h3>
          <p>Ship final store assets, coordinate creator beats, and ensure your official pages outrank imitation content for critical queries.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-card">
          <div class="timeline-badge">Live Ops</div>
          <h3>Sustain Momentum</h3>
          <p>Publish seasonal content, capture changelogs, and maintain category rankings. Keep guides fresh as metas evolve.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Tools We Use -->
  <section class="tools-section">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Tools We <span>Use</span></h2>
        <p>We integrate with your stack so reporting is simple and decisions are fast.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="tools-grid">
        <div class="tool-card"><i class="fab fa-steam"></i><span>Steamworks</span></div>
        <div class="tool-card"><i class="fab fa-apple"></i><span>App Store Connect</span></div>
        <div class="tool-card"><i class="fab fa-google-play"></i><span>Google Play Console</span></div>
        <div class="tool-card"><i class="fab fa-google"></i><span>Search Console</span></div>
        <div class="tool-card"><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i><span>GA4 & Looker</span></div>
        <div class="tool-card"><i class="fas fa-search"></i><span>Ahrefs / Semrush</span></div>
        <div class="tool-card"><i class="fab fa-youtube"></i><span>YouTube Studio</span></div>
        <div class="tool-card"><i class="fab fa-discord"></i><span>Discord & Reddit</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="faq-section gaming-faq">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Gaming SEO <span>FAQs</span></h2>
        <p>Honest answers based on years of working with game teams of every size.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-list">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
            <span>How long before we see results?</span>
            <i class="fas fa-plus"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Early wins often show within 4–8 weeks (brand protection, technical fixes). Competitive category gains typically build over 3–6 months as content, links, and store signals compound.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
            <span>Do you handle ASO as well as website SEO?</span>
            <i class="fas fa-plus"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Yes. We optimize both app store listings and websites. Discovery is multi‑surface for games, so we align titles, descriptions, tags, creatives, and on‑site content to the same strategy.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
            <span>We’re a small indie. Is SEO overkill?</span>
            <i class="fas fa-plus"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Not at all. We right‑size the work. A tight keyword strategy, a fast landing page, and a dozen helpful guides can meaningfully lift wishlists and organic installs without bloating your workload.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
            <span>Can SEO help at launch if we’re late?</span>
            <i class="fas fa-plus"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Yes. We prioritize high‑impact changes: fix indexing, secure brand SERPs, optimize store assets, publish priority guides, and coordinate creator coverage so official pages win the click.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
            <span>How do you measure success beyond rankings?</span>
            <i class="fas fa-plus"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>We track the full path: impressions → clicks → wishlists/installs → retention. Reporting focuses on what content and store elements move players, not vanity metrics.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
            <span>Do you work with esports and live‑service titles?</span>
            <i class="fas fa-plus"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Absolutely. We maintain continuous content, surface patch cadence, and help creators cover updates. SEO becomes part of your live‑ops rhythm.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Banner -->
  <section class="cta-banner-section">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="cta-banner">
        <h3>Let’s make your game easier to find — and harder to ignore.</h3>
        <div class="cta-actions">
          <a href="/contact/" class="cta-button primary">Talk to a strategist</a>
          <a href="/case-studies/" class="cta-button secondary">View case studies</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <ContactSection />
  <Footer slot="footer" />
</MainLayout>

<style>
  :root {
    --brand-primary: #1a1a1a;
    --brand-accent: #f97316;
    --brand-secondary: #2563eb;
    --brand-dark: #1f2937;
    --brand-soft: #6b7280;
    --brand-light: #f8fafc;
    --brand-white: #ffffff;
  }

  /* Gaming Icon Grid (used in Hero visual slot) */
  .hero-image-container {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 400px;
  }

  .gaming-icon-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .gaming-icon {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
    border-radius: 20px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    color: white;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    animation: iconFloat 4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .gaming-icon:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0s; }
  .gaming-icon:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.5s; }
  .gaming-icon:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 1s; }
  .gaming-icon:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 1.5s; }
  .gaming-icon:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 2s; }
  .gaming-icon:nth-child(6) { animation-delay: 2.5s; }

  @keyframes iconFloat {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
  }

  .gaming-icon:hover {
    transform: scale(1.1) translateY(-5px);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
  }

  /* Why Gaming Section */
  .why-gaming-section {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: #f8fafc;
  }

  .gaming-explanation {
    max-width: 4xl;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .gaming-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 2rem;
    background: white;
    padding: 3rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .gaming-card .gaming-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f97316, #FF6B35);
    border-radius: 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: white;
    font-size: 2rem;
  }

  .gaming-text p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--brand-dark);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .gaming-text p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* Features Section */
  .features-section {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: white;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--brand-dark);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-header h2 span {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f97316, #4285F4);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .section-header p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--brand-soft);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .feature-card {
    position: relative;
    background: white;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    transition: all 0.4s ease;
    border: 2px solid #f0f0f0;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .feature-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 5px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f97316, #FF6B35);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.4s ease;
  }

  .feature-card:hover::before {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .feature-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.15);
    border-color: rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.3);
  }

  .feature-icon {
    width: 90px;
    height: 90px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f97316, #FF6B35);
    border-radius: 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: white;
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.25);
    transition: all 0.4s ease;
  }

  .feature-card:hover .feature-icon {
    transform: scale(1.1) rotate(5deg);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.35);
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--brand-dark);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .feature-card p {
    color: var(--brand-soft);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Shared Section Header */
  .section-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .section-header h2 {
    margin: 0 0 .5rem 0;
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw, 2.25rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--brand-dark);
  }
  .section-header h2 span {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f97316, #4285F4);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    color: transparent;
  }
  .section-header p { color: var(--brand-soft); max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }

  /* Services Offerings Section */
  .services-offerings-section {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: #f8fafc;
  }

  .offerings-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .offering-card {
    position: relative;
    background: #ffffff;
    padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 18px;
    border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .offering-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f97316, #FF6B35);
  }

  .offering-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.15);
    border-color: #f97316;
  }

  .offering-icon {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 16px;
    color: #fff;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f97316, #FF6B35);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.25);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .offering-card:hover .offering-icon {
    transform: scale(1.1);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.35);
  }

  .offering-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--brand-dark);
    margin-bottom: .5rem;
  }

  .offering-card p { color: var(--brand-soft); }

  .learn-more-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.1), rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.1));
    color: #f97316;
    padding: 0.625rem 1.25rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
